Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.26,0:00:11.00,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Nakagawa Hirotaka"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.33,0:00:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nakagawa Hirotaka, and\NI transferred here from Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.45,0:00:11.10,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,東京から転校してきた中川広孝だ　宜しくな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.33,0:00:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.33,0:00:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! Tokyo scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:13.17,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ふん　東京もんが
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hirotaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:18.11,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,広孝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.34,0:00:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuya? Kuya, is that you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.40,0:00:19.02,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,空也
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:20.76,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,空也なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.24,0:00:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a fateful reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:24.27,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それは運命の再会であった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika sees no problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:27.76,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,問題ありませんね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.95,0:00:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Okay, we're good.\NLet's go to the next scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:30.34,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よし　オーケーだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:32.17,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,次のシーン行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.42,0:00:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:35.53,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,準備はいいか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.85,0:00:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:36.71,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,オーケー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.21,0:00:38.50,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お　重い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.52,0:00:42.14,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(910,218)\c&H95BBD0&\3c&H385348&}The Moon Rises\Nin the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, lights... camera... action!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.72,0:00:39.87,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　本番
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:42.05,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よーい　アクション
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.30,0:00:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:46.07,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前　生意気なんぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.37,0:00:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How dare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:48.14,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,な　何だと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you say "how dare you"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:49.69,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だとは何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.87,0:00:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.95,0:00:51.01,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,カット
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.44,0:00:52.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　次は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.44,0:00:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, the next one is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.94,0:00:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yozora-{\i1}sempai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.06,0:00:56.26,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,夜空先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.14,0:00:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun is setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.21,0:00:59.21,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もうかなり日が傾いています
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.65,0:01:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything else we shoot now\Nwon't match our other footage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:02.32,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これ以上撮っても絵が繋がりませんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's that, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.74,0:01:04.67,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,仕方ない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll pick it up tomorrow!\NMeet in the club room after school!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.31,0:01:07.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よし　続きは明日だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:09.46,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,放課後また部室に集合
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.72,0:01:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We're running low on time, so don't be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.77,0:01:11.86,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もう時間がないから遅れるなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.13,0:01:13.46,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.56,0:01:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.61,0:01:14.86,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,声が小さい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.99,0:01:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.06,0:01:16.48,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.78,0:01:32.74,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be My Friend{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:35.01,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, you played dumb{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:36.01,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be My Side{\i}
