Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.10,0:01:51.93,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Haganai NEXT"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.76,0:01:56.00,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's more than I imagined... every{\i}\N{\i1}day's a roller coaster{\i}
