Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.53,0:02:28.90,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll walk another step toward your side{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:31.20,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I can take your hand{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:32.30,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be My Friend{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:34.37,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, I'm always gazing at the sky{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:35.54,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be My Side{\i}
