Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No scenes with Kotaro today either, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:58.66,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今日も小太郎の出番はなしか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:01.18,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと残念な気もするけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.77,0:03:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But being part of the crew is more\Nfun than I thought, so I guess it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:04.85,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まっ　裏方ってもやってみると案外面白いから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:05.53,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いいか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, those must be the\Nscore rankings from finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:11.48,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,期末試験の順位表か
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:22.52,Default - Style 06,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(666,240)}Second-Year Exam Rankings
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:22.52,Default - Style 06,,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,400)}Kashiwazaki Sena
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:20.19,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,900点満点中895点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,895 out of 900?! How does\Nanyone even get a score like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:22.85,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうやったら取れるんだ　そんな点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:23.79,Default - Style 06,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,378)}Mikazuki Yozora
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And Yozora's first in our class, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:27.08,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,夜空は夜空で うちのクラスじゃ一番だし
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Grrrrrr... Grrrrrr...\N- What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:30.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:36.18,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何ですか　君は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:38.68,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,えっと　俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You're Kashiwazaki Sena's boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.21,0:03:42.28,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,君は柏崎星奈の彼氏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Grrrrrr!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Kashiwazaki Sena... that\Nwoman is definitely my enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:48.93,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,柏崎星奈　やっぱりあの女は自分の敵です
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.11,0:03:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, so who are {\i1}you?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:51.99,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,えっと　そういうお前は誰なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You don't know who I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:54.93,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,自分を知らないですと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:04:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I should've expected an\Nassociate of Kashiwazaki Sena's to be rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:59.75,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱり柏崎星奈の関係者だけあって失礼ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you famous or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.71,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何か有名だったりするのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.73,0:04:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yusa Aoi, Year 2, Class 3!\NI'm the student council treasurer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:06.31,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,2年3組遊佐葵　生徒会会計です
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I ranked #2 on these tests!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:08.17,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今回の試験では二位でした
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.07,0:04:13.27,Default - Style 06,,0,0,0,,{\pos(506,260)}Kashiwazaki Sena
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.07,0:04:13.27,Default - Style 06,,0,0,0,,{\pos(490,500)}Yusa Aoi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:12.79,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,3組　星奈と同じクラス
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's Class 3, she's\Nin the same class as Sena.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're #2 in our whole grade\Nand a student council officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:16.20,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,学年二位で生徒会の役員か
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:17.44,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すごいんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That condescending attitude\Nis extremely obnoxious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:21.13,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,その上から目線が非常に腹立たしいです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been Kashiwazaki Sena's\Nrunner-up since last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:24.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうせ自分は去年からずっと柏崎星奈の下ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about last year, but\NI still think you're doing really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:26.98,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,去年のことは知らんけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:29.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも十分立派だと思うぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just tough, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:31.06,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,相手が悪いだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I still want to win! At least\Nin test scores, if nothing else!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:33.86,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも勝ちたいのです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:35.88,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,せめてテストの成績くらいは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Glamorous looks, outstanding\Ngrades, great at all sports,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:41.41,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あのきらきらとした外見の上　成績優秀　スポーツ万能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:43.74,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,その上　お金持ちのお嬢様
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and{\i} she's a rich little princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've heard this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:47.29,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どっかで聞いたような評価だな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I know for a fact that the world\Ncalls those like Kashiwazaki Sena
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:48.68,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,自分は知っています
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.27,0:04:51.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,柏崎星奈のような人のことを世の中では
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.11,0:04:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"people with real lives."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:54.27,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,「リア充」と呼ぶのだと言うことを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She gets to have a real life\N{\i1}and{\i} a boyfriend on top of that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:58.30,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ただでさえ「リア充」なくせに彼氏までいるなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.86,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,人生勝ち組過ぎるではありませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:05:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's patently unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, slow down. I'm not dating Sena!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:02.22,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だからちょっと待って
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:04.42,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は星奈と付き合ってるわけじゃないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't fool me. You use\Nher first name with no honorific...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:06.81,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ごまかしても無駄なのです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:11.15,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,下の名前を呼び捨てするなんて特別な関係に決まっています
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you've obviously got a special relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All the boys in our class use "-{\i1}sama{\i0}" for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:16.07,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,自分のクラスの男子達は柏崎星奈のことを皆「様」付けて呼びます
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use. She's just not listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:18.89,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,駄目だ　こいつ聞く耳持ってない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly... I'm fighting\Nlike mad to surpass her,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:23.01,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まったく　自分が必死で追い抜こうと頑張ってるあいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and meanwhile she gets\Nherself a cool boyfriend like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:25.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,柏崎星奈はこんな格好いい彼氏と
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:27.01,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,羨ましいです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, when you say "cool,"\Nare you talking about {\i1}me{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:32.07,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あのさ　もしかして格好いいって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:33.61,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺がか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What, do you see anybody else standing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:36.17,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかに誰がいるのですか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And any way you look at it, you're cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:38.95,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どう見ても君は格好いいのですが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.59,0:05:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's that understated blond\Nhair you clearly take such pains to dye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:43.25,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,明らかに拘りをもって染めている渋い感じの金髪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And you wear your pants rolled\Nup, because you've got fashion!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:45.98,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ズボンのすそなんか曲げちゃっておしゃれさんです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I know for a fact that the\Nworld calls cool guys like you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:47.73,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,自分は知っています
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:50.67,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,君のような格好いい男子のことを世間では
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"bad-boy chic," you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:52.58,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,「ちょい悪系」と呼ぶのでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nobody's ever talked\Nabout me like that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:57.37,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなふうに言われたのは初めてだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:06:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you making that funny face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:06:00.09,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何面白い顔をしているのですか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you've got a sense\Nof humor on top of the cool factor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:03.04,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,格好いい上にユーモアまで備えているなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're obviously the kind of awesome\Nboyfriend suited to Little Miss Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:07.80,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あの完璧すぎる柏崎星奈に相応しい素敵な彼氏ではないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm displeased yet jealous! Completely envious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:11.65,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まったくもって不愉快もあり　羨ましくもあり　妬ましいです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.86,0:06:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.65,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,自分はこれで失礼します
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yusa Aoi, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:20.29,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,遊佐葵か
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've met yet another weirdo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:24.15,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,また変わったやつと出会っちまったな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:30.66,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おーす
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're all alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:33.69,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あれ　一人だけか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yozora and Rika left. They said\Nsomething about location scouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:37.04,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,夜空と理科はロケハンだとか言って出て行ったわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently they want a shot\Nof the sun setting into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:39.71,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,太陽は海に沈む絵がほしいんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... Oh, I just remembered: I ran into\Na girl named Yusa Aoi on my way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:42.18,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:45.60,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ここに来る途中で遊佐葵ってやつに会ったんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's Yusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:46.84,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,遊佐って誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "who"?!\NShe's a girl in your class!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:49.99,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,誰って　お前と同じクラスの女子だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.83,0:06:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She's short, and she's got sort of reddish hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:54.08,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何か背が低くて　赤っぽい色の髪のやつ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, that does sound kind of familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:57.58,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,確かそんなようなのもいた気がするわね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.80,0:07:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,At least memorize the names of your classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:07:00.43,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,クラスメイトの名前くらい覚えとけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I memorized the girls who\Nsit next to me and behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:03.61,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,後ろと隣の席の女子の名前は覚えたわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that it paid off any.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:05.26,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,覚えて損したけど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:06.82,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何かあったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told you before: There are\Nonly two types of girls in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:08.60,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,前に言ったでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:11.43,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,世の中には2種類の女子しかいないの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:14.24,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(170,450)}Yayoi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:14.24,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(86,560)}Yeah! Let's go together on Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:14.75,Default,,0,0,200,,- Great girls I hit it off with, and those other bitches.\N- Yeah! Let's go together on Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:14.47,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしと仲良くしてくれる素敵な女の子と
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:16.92,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(170,450)}Rui
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:16.92,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(86,560)}I don't want to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:16.86,Default,,0,0,200,,- Great girls I hit it off with, and those other bitches.\N- I don't want to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:16.44,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,してくれないメス犬よ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:19.93,Default,,0,0,200,,Why should I have to remember\Nall those mongrels' names?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:20.75,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして駄犬の名前をこのあたしがいちいち覚えないといけないの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:19.76,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,224)\bord4\fs42\an7\pos(376,172)}1.   Don't be like that. Come with us!!\N\N\N2.   Should we go somewhere else, then?\N\N\N3.   Fine, don't come! Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:21.33,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(200,450)}Sena-{\i1}sama{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:21.33,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(86,560)}Fine, don't come! Moron!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, don't come! Moron!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So she calls her classmates "mongrels"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.80,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,クラスメイトを駄犬呼ばわりか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, evidently this Yusa girl's name
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:25.93,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一応その遊佐ってやつ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,has been right below yours\Non every single test ranking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:30.09,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,試験の順位発表でずっとお前の下に名前があるらしいんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I care about\Nother people's rankings?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:32.32,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,知らないわよ　他人の順位なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they even posted, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:35.17,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ていうか　それってどこで発表されてるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.27,0:07:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,On the bulletin board, obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:37.23,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,掲示板に張り出されてるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.38,0:07:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:38.79,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never {\i1}looked{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:40.35,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,見たことないのかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell my rank from the paper that\Nhas our percentiles and stuff, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:44.54,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だって　自分の順位の偏差値とか書いてある紙でわかるじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The only important\Nthing is that I come in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:47.48,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,大事なのはあたしが一番ってことだけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:49.11,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前すげえわ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.35,0:07:49.80,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of studying do you\Nusually do? Do you have a tutor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:52.54,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前普段どんな勉強してるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:53.89,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,家庭教師とかか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't study except for going\Nto class and doing my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:56.95,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,勉強なんて授業と宿題しかやってないわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?! What about for tests, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:59.55,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,マジすか　じゃ試験勉強は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That time with you was my only time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:02.16,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この前やったのが最初で最後ね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That was kind of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:04.34,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あれはちょっと楽しかったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah... I guess it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:07.23,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.31,0:08:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Kodaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:08.55,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それで小鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen with that Yusa girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:11.48,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,その遊佐とか言うのがどうかしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:13.33,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もういや
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:14.39,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ　そう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:19.81,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつ　本当に興味あること以外にはとことん興味がないんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She really doesn't care at all\Nabout stuff she's not interested in...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet when she likes something,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:24.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そのくせ気にいたものに対しては周囲がドン引きする勢いでずっぱしゅう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,she gets so into it she makes\Neverybody else uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to Yozora, even if she\Ndoesn't like it she gets practically criminal...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:29.22,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,気にいたものじゃなくても夜空に対しては犯罪滑々
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I guess the sneak\Nphoto thing really {\i1}is{\i} criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:31.64,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　盗撮とか完全に犯罪か
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She lives however she pleases\Nand does whatever she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:35.29,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どこまでも自由奔放勝手気まま
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's got the huge talent and\Nfamily circumstances to get away with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:37.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな生き方が出来てしまうだけの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.96,0:08:42.32,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ぶっちぎりの能力や境遇を備えた　生まれながらのお姫様
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a born princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's only natural for\Nthe other girls to hate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:45.88,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかの女子が敵愾心を抱くのも無理ないかもな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it,\Ngetting to hang out with her so casually
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.22,0:08:50.70,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなやつとこんなふうに気楽に付き合えるってのは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,might actually be an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:52.70,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,案外光栄のことなのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We found the perfect location!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:56.95,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,最高のロケションが見つかりました
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:09:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going straight out\Nto film it. Let's go, Meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:58.75,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐに撮影だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:08:59.89,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,行くぞ　肉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:03.35,夏雪日文旁白-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょ…　まだ　セーブしてなかったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- I hadn't saved yet!\N- You get ready too, Kodaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:03.33,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鷹もすぐに用意しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:04.77,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はい はい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shooting time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:07.69,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(910,200)\c&HC0D1CF&\3c&H385348&\bord0}The Moon Rises\Nin the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And... action!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:07.86,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よーい　アクション
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Grit your teeth, Hirotaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:10.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,広孝　歯を食いしばれ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:16.00,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,く　空也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kuya...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:17.43,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,カット
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:21.43,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はい　オーケーです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you sure this is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:24.11,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おいおい　本当に大丈夫なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:25.26,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何がですか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- How was it?\N- The background is obviously a park.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:29.30,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,背景　思いっきり公園だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Not bad.\N- The background is obviously a park.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.33,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,心配御無用です
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika will turn it into a perfect beach later with CG.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:34.85,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あとはCGで見事な砂浜に仕上げて見せますから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:36.06,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,乞うご期待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:42.64,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ理科は編集作業があるので　これで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Rika needs to go\Nedit this, so she'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what she said, but can she\Nreally manage it? She's no CG expert...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:48.08,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,とか言ってたけど　何とかなるものなのか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:50.89,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,CGだって万能じゃなかろうに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, if it isn't Kodaka-{\i1}kun!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:53.24,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鷹君ではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:55.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,理事長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,President?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fancy meeting you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:57.56,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,奇遇だな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:59.27,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうも　こんにちは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:09:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This school festival atmosphere\Nis quite pleasant, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:05.89,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いいものだな　この学園祭の空気というものは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:08.10,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうですね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your club is doing a\Nmovie, if I recall correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:15.70,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,確か君達は映画を撮っているんだったな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:16.78,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Movies are nice. Hayato used\Nto drag me to them all the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:18.60,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,映画はいいものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:22.22,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私も昔　よく隼人のやつに連れられて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,President?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:24.91,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,理事長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:26.42,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　なんでもない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what's this movie like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:29.98,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それより　君達はどんな映画を撮っているのかね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sena never told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:32.38,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,星奈から聞いてないんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have many chances\Nto speak with her, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:36.54,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あれとはあまり話す機会がなくてな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:37.77,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to see it when it's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:43.07,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,完成したら是非見せてもらいたいものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel a little shy about\Nhaving someone I know watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:46.41,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,知り合いに見られるのはちょっと恥ずかしいですね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Kodaka-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:48.24,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,時に　小鷹君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:48.74,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How is your relationship\Nwith Sena coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:52.50,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,星奈との交際のほうも順調かね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.74,0:10:54.92,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,えっと　あの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you're embarrassed\Nto talk about it with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.39,0:10:59.24,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やはりこういう話をするのは気恥ずかしいかね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not that I'm embarrassed, it's\Njust... what do you mean, "relationship"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:01.53,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　気恥ずかしいって言うか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:05.19,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,交際って　何の事ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you don't need to play dumb about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:08.34,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何も惚ける必要はないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... No, really, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:11.81,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,えっと　いや　本当に何の事です
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Sena are dating, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:21.41,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,君と星奈は交際しているのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:22.77,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,してないですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:27.53,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あーれー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Something urgent has come up.\NI'll see you another day, Kodaka-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:32.88,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,急用が出来た
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:35.31,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それでは小鷹君　また後日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:47.84,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a funny guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:52.78,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,面白いな　あのおじさん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:12:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:12:00.01,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おーす
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kodaka, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:01.65,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鷹　ちょっと来なさい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:05.37,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どこへ行くのだ　肉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to do something. We'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.93,0:12:07.80,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと用事　すぐ戻るから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sena!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:09.75,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おい　星奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:18.82,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あつー
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? What did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:22.24,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,で　何の話だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:28.89,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何か　あたしとあんた　パパに付き合ってると思われてたみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like Daddy\Nthought you and I were dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:31.01,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱりその話か
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that to me\Nyesterday, too. It surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:35.76,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も昨日理事長にそんなこと言われて驚いたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:38.88,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしてそんな話になってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, um... How do I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:43.45,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　そのう　なんと言いますか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't glare at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:45.86,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そ　そんな睨まないでよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to glare at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:48.33,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,睨んでるつもりはないんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, you remember how we all\Nwent to the amusement park?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:51.84,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,えっと　前に皆で遊園地に行ったじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:53.71,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　行ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:57.27,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あの時のチケット　パパからもらったんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I got those tickets from Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:12:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:12:59.14,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, when he\Ngave them to me, I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:05.49,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,その時あたしね　言っちゃったのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Now I can have\NKobato-{\i1}chan{\i} for my little sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:09.87,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これで小鳩ちゃんを妹にできるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:11.51,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Daddy got the wrong idea from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:14.89,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それで　パパが勘違いしちゃったのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.76,0:13:17.05,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,意味わかんねえぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:18.83,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もう　察しがわるいわね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, you're so dense! If you and\NI got... m-m-m-married or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:19.95,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたとあたしが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:24.05,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そのう　け　け　け　結婚とかしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:26.60,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしの妹ってことになるでしょうが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously she'd be my sister, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:27.75,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Married{\i0}?! I mean, yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:29.82,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それはそうなるが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:31.81,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あの時はテンション上がっちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time I was so excited,\NI didn't think too deeply about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:33.50,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,深く考えなかったんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I remember him saying lots of stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:37.13,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そういえばパパ　いろいろ言ってたのよね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Like "Are there plans for\NKobato-{\i1}kun{\i} to become your sister?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:41.56,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鳩君がお前の妹になる予定があるのかっとか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.97,0:13:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and "How is your relationship\Nprogressing?" and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:44.80,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,仲は順調に進展しているのかっとかって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And what did you answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:47.82,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,で　お前はそれになんて答えたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't you worry!\NI've totally got this!" I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:49.82,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,「ばっちりよ　任しといて」っで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha, it turns out he meant my\Nrelationship with {\i1}you,{\i} not Kobato-{\i1}chan!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:54.45,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　あれって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:55.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鳩ちゃんとの仲じゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.22,0:13:58.20,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたとの仲って意味だったのね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:01.16,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前なあS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I am deeply ashamed of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:03.68,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,面目しだいも御座いませぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least you've explained\Nthings to him now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:08.56,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,でもまあ　理事長にちゃんと説明したんだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. As long as he gets that it\Nwas all a misunderstanding, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:10.56,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:13.84,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと勘違いだってわかってもらえたんなら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:14.64,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もういいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.61,0:14:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel kind of bad for the President,\Nbut I'm glad it's all straightened out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:17.69,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,理事長にはちょっと申し訳ないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:19.44,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,誤解が解けてよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, here's what I wanted to talk to you about...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:22.52,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それで　ここからが本題なんだけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What? There's more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:24.91,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まだなんかあるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. And just so you\Nknow, this part is {\i1}not{\i} my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:29.88,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,言っとくけど　これはあたしかなんかやらかしたわけじゃないからね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something I only just now found\Nout, because of this whole mess...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:34.65,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今回のことが切っ掛けで　あたしも初めてしたことなんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:38.55,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしとあんた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...are apparently engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:42.11,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,婚約してるみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Kodaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:46.30,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫　小鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:52.29,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんかね　あたしとあんたがまだ物心付く前に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.87,0:14:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy says that back when\Nwe were too young to remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:55.63,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしのパパとあんたのパパが約束したんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,he and your daddy made a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, we're what you'd call "betrothed."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:58.14,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,つまりいいなずけってやつね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:14:59.76,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いいなずけ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Betrothed?! This is like\Nsomething out of a soap opera...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:02.01,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなドラマみたいな設定が
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:04.62,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何か誓約書みたいなのもあって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They even wrote up a pact,\Nand it has our thumbprints on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:06.70,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしたちの拇印も押してあったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They took it that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:08.74,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなものまで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.89,0:15:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Our prints were really tiny. It was pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:12.41,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんかね　すごい小さな指紋で　可愛かったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.73,0:15:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? I don't remember this at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:16.12,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか　まったく覚えてない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't either! But look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:18.30,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしだって　覚えてないわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:20.02,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,でも　ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:22.05,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like you and I met a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:26.16,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしとあんた　ずっと昔に会ったことあるみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:27.38,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,マジでか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels kind of weird, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:31.01,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何か変な感じね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, totally...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:34.04,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, setting that aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:41.14,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　それはともかくだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.99,0:15:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,About the marriage thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:43.53,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,結婚の話だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.10,0:15:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,An engagement we didn't make\Nourselves isn't anything to worry about, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:48.35,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺達の意志と無関係に決められた婚約なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:49.93,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,気にすることないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:53.24,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そ　そうよね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just something our\Ndads are randomly saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:56.43,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなの　パパ達が勝手に言ってるだけなんだもんね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:16:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I dunno about "our"...\NI doubt my dad remembers the pact.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:59.02,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ああいや　「達」って言うか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:03.06,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の親父のほうは多分この約束覚えてないと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.01,0:16:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:04.04,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So, no need for us to sweat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:07.19,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,つうわけで　この件は気にする必要なしだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right! We won't sweat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:09.06,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そ　そうよね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:10.65,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,気にしない　気にしない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:13.34,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっとだけ惜しい気もするけど
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it almost seems like a pity...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.69,0:16:15.98,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんでもないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we're not engaged, I'll make\NKobato-{\i1}chan{\i} my sister all by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:18.23,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたとの婚約なんてなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:21.43,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,自分の力で小鳩ちゃんを妹にして見せるんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose I can\Nget you to give up on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:24.82,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それはいい加減諦めてくれませんかね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go back to the club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:28.12,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そんじゃ　部室に戻ろうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:31.24,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あたし達はいいんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We{\i} may be fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little worried about\Nwhat that moron will think.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:36.01,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あの馬鹿がどう思うかだけ　ちょっと気になるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like we have to tell\Nher, right? It's irrelevant anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:40.00,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,別に言う必要ないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:42.43,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,関係ないことだし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:46.04,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そっかな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:49.53,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late! What were you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:54.78,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,遅い
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.19,0:16:56.46,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何をやっていたのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.34,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと野暮用よ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:17:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing too important. Now, shall we go film?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:00.01,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ　早く撮影に行きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:05.42,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まあいい　では行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. Today we're starting\Nwith the baseball field scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.35,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今日はグランドのシーンからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.85,0:17:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for more movie-making!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:12.47,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今日も映画やるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:13.51,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,マリア
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Big Brother! I'm gonna\Nmake a movie with Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:15.21,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:17.75,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今日もお兄ちゃんと一緒に映画撮るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I feel\Nlike I'm forgetting something...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:23.88,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そういえば なんか忘れてるような気が
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've got Sena-{\i1}san,{\i}\Nso I guess that's out...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:27.89,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　星奈さんがいるからしょうがないか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When Kate said "that's out," did she mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:32.73,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ケイトが言ってたしょうがないってのは　もしかして
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:33.65,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you and Sena really getting\Nmarried? The hag said so yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:36.69,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,昨日婆に聞いたんだけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:39.95,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃんは星奈と結婚するって本当なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.86,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,婚約者って言うのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The word is "fiancée," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're so grown up if\Nyou've got a fiancée, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.11,0:17:44.43,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,婚約者がいるので
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:47.58,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱりお兄ちゃんは大人なのです　凄いな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So grown up! Way grown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:52.01,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,大人　大人だな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.81,0:17:55.21,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ど　どういうことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.30,0:18:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Betrothed... And the two\Nof them met a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:06.75,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いいなずけ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:10.10,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも二人は昔会っていたか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But hey, it's totally\Nirrelevant to us now! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:14.77,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　今の俺達には何の関係もない話だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:15.76,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:17.87,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうね　そのとおりよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! That's exactly right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Rika-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:20.68,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なあ　理科さんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Yozora-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:23.22,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何ですかの　夜空さんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Which relationship is closer,\Nchildhood friends or betrotheds?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:28.48,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,幼なじみといいなずけって　どっちのほうが関係が深いかな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.86,0:18:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika believes most\Npeople would say betrotheds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.93,0:18:32.45,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一般的に考えていいなずけだと思いますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:35.09,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially since they met as children.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:38.46,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも昔会っていたらしいですからね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,One could say they're\Nchildhood friends, couldn't one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:41.39,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,幼なじみであるとも言えますね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:43.53,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.59,0:18:45.60,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もう　鬱陶しいわね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're{\i} saying it doesn't matter, so\Nwhat are {\i1}you{\i} losing confidence for, idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:48.87,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,当のあたし達がどうでもいい話だって言ってんのに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:51.98,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんでそんなにうじうじしてんのよ　馬鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Meat...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:56.21,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,に　肉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,For Pete's sake! Come on, let's go film!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:03.73,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ もう　はら　さっさと撮影行くわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sena-{\i1}sempai{\i} is right, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:10.11,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　星奈先輩の言うとおりですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no use worrying about the\Npast and promises parents made, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:13.45,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,昔のこととか　親が決めた約束とか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:16.12,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなの気にしては仕方ないじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's focus on the future, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:17.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,前を向いていきましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we filming today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.54,0:19:21.17,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今日はどこで取るのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:29.63,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何かもう　どうでもいいや
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. I don't care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:45.47,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お　お兄ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Kotaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.94,0:19:47.77,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした　小太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:51.10,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,広兄が　広兄が大変だんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Hiro-{\i1}nii!{\i} He's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:19:52.01,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.18,0:19:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:54.13,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はい　カット
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.45,0:19:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:56.41,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:19:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.29,0:20:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Her mind is somewhere else, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.70,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,上の空だな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we move on to the next scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:04.98,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,次のシーンに行きましょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.09,0:20:10.40,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,疲れた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiya, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:18.98,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やー　お兄ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:22.17,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前なあ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Today was a train wreck thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:26.20,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前のせいで今日大変だったんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- Pardon?\N- Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:27.92,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:29.04,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,待って
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:32.02,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それはすまなかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.22,0:20:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, it's not like we're the only ones
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:36.03,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,でもお兄ちゃんと星奈さんが婚約してることを知ってるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,who know you and Sena-{\i1}san{\i} are engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:37.84,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,別に私達だけじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.89,0:20:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:41.31,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,天馬さん　ことあることに喋ってるからね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.39,0:20:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Pegasus-{\i1}san{\i} talks about\Nit every chance he gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd bet almost all of the sisters\Nand faculty here know about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:45.77,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,学園のシスターや教員はほとんど全員知ってるだろうし
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and there might even be students who know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.02,0:20:48.25,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,生徒の中にも知ってる子はいるかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, that guy's got a big mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:51.13,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あのおじさん　口軽いな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He was probably really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:53.91,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よっぽと嬉しかったんだろうね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.22,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, so that was just\NPegasus jumping to conclusions...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:58.26,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あれが天馬さんの早とちりだったんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.28,0:21:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:20:59.87,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:01.36,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何でもないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I hear you guys are making a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:05.87,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ところでお兄ちゃん達　映画を撮ってるんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.98,0:21:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:08.28,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな内容なんだい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.79,0:21:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't make heads or\Ntails of Maria's explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:11.75,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,マリアの話じゃ　どうも要領を得なくてね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.76,0:21:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:13.57,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so it's a coming-of-age story\Ncentered around a transfer student.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:16.07,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.78,0:21:19.61,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,転校生を中心にした青春ものか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:23.35,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だか　「坂道の上の太陽」みたいな話だね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me of {\i1}Boys Over the Slope.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Boys Over the Slope{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:25.65,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,「坂道の上の太陽」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's a Japanese\Ncoming-of-age movie, a cult classic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:29.86,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うん　知る人ぞ知る和製青春映画の名作でね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:31.86,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私もかなり好きなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.11,0:21:34.14,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃんもぜひ見てみるといいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You should check it out, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, maybe I will! It could\Nbe good reference material.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:38.56,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,参考になるかもしれないし　見てみるか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.13,0:21:54.37,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お　お兄ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.47,0:21:55.77,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした　広太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.47,0:21:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Kotaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.03,0:21:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Taka-{\i1}nii!{\i} He's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.07,0:21:58.85,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,孝兄が　孝兄が大変なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.47,0:22:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.51,0:22:00.24,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.47,0:22:05.81,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\an8\pos(864,376)}The Moon Rises in the Sky\NBy: Mikazuki Yozora\NDraft 3
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you, Yozora... Your script...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:02.24,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.56,0:22:03.32,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.63,0:22:05.67,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の脚本
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.81,0:22:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...is totally cribbed from this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:10.03,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ぱっくりじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.83,0:22:34.22,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,光ったはずの星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:34.27,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A stray cloud blocks my view{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.27,0:22:37.44,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,迷った雲が邪魔して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.27,0:22:39.78,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of the star I know should be shining there{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.48,0:22:39.54,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,見えなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.78,0:22:43.27,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I believe in?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.93,0:22:42.83,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何を信じたらいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.91,0:22:47.12,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was on my way to breaking{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.99,0:22:47.25,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,不安定すぎる世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.12,0:22:52.96,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The treasure bred in this all too changeable world{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.27,0:22:52.35,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,育った宝物壊しかけてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.96,0:22:57.06,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I was afraid of losing it{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:55.91,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なくすのが怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.03,0:22:58.74,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,不条理だって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.06,0:23:00.36,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those days of sighing "This is absurd"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.75,0:23:00.05,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ため息つき
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.07,0:23:03.41,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうにかどうで足掻いてた日々
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:03.60,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And flailing inside my birdcage{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.60,0:23:09.77,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were gazing up at the same sky{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.66,0:23:07.82,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,同じ空を見上げてたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.10,0:23:09.75,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.77,0:23:13.07,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,君の手を握った時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.77,0:23:16.11,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I gripped your hand,{\i}\N{\i1}you gripped back, didn't you?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.09,0:23:16.26,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,握り返してくれたね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.11,0:23:22.65,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These joined hands are stronger than any wings{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.30,0:23:19.40,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,繋がったこの手は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.51,0:23:22.87,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな羽より強いんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.65,0:23:29.23,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can fly higher even without wings{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.89,0:23:26.02,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,翼だってなくったって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.05,0:23:29.31,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと高く飛べるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.23,0:23:32.60,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I know we'll be okay trying now{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.33,0:23:32.55,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,きっと今なら大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.58,0:23:37.67,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,大空輝く星を掴もう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:38.33,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's grab the stars twinkling in the sky{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.14,0:23:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I shall tell you exactly what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.16,0:23:44.52,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あ　ありのまま起こったことを話すぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:47.47,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私は星奈と小鷹が交際していると思っていたんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.58,0:23:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Sena and Kodaka-{\i1}kun{\i}\Nwere dating, but it wasn't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.47,0:23:48.82,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,実はそんなことはなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:50.94,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,な　何を言ってるのかわからないと思うが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.85,0:23:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You may not understand what\NI'm saying, but I don't really get this either.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.94,0:23:52.71,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺もどういうことなのかわからない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.68,0:23:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.71,0:23:54.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まあまあ　落ち付いてくださいな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.12,0:23:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem happy, Kate-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.13,0:23:56.65,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だか嬉しそうだな　ケイト君
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.65,0:23:58.77,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　そんなことないですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.69,0:23:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.69,0:24:00.63,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そ　そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.76,0:24:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.37,0:24:10.72,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\an8\pos(640,373)}"{\c&H8728E4&}The Sad-Case King {\c&HFFFFFF&}and\N{\c&H10E5B0&}the {\c&HFFFFFF&}Stone-Cold {\c&H0BEAF8&}Story{\c&HFFFFFF&}"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.13,0:24:03.47,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,次回　「残念王と笑えない話」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.16,0:24:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: "The Sad-Case\NKing and the Stone-Cold Story."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:06.12,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,前途多難だね　お兄ちゃんも
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother's got a rough life, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.18,0:24:08.23,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こりゃ私にもワンチャンあるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.20,0:24:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I have a chance now?
